{"tid":143863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美動物園直播長頸鹿分娩　動保組織舉報裸露色情　YouTube影片一度下架","createTime":"2017-03-05T03:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T04:13:36.000Z","uid":50769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18255ba5331c5ff0e262759e965b0fe7bbd876b1","tid":143863,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"美國紐約州一個動物園計劃透過YouTube直播園內明星長頸鹿的分娩過程，惟遭動物保育組織舉報，影片含有裸露及色情內容，令影片一度被YouTube禁播。園方斥保育組織做法過火，妨礙公眾教育。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：特朗普暗批巴黎不安全　法總統奧朗德：不應挑戰盟友　暗轟美槍械制度<br />\n<br />\n今次風波的主角、15歲雌性長頸鹿April來自動物園Animal Adventure Park，即將誕下第4頭幼崽。園主帕奇（Jordan Patch）上周三（22日）起在YouTube直播April獸舍情況，讓網民可即時觀看April分娩的神奇時刻，盼助公眾了解長頸鹿生態，加強對保護野生長頸鹿的關注。影片吸引多達2000萬次點擊觀賞。不過，有動物保育組織向YouTube舉報，指片段含有裸露及色情內容，違反YouTube使用守則，上周四直播被迫中斷。<br />\n<br />\n帕奇對事件大感不滿，認為有關「極端保育組織」可以不接受直播長頸鹿分娩，但強令停播的做法並不恰當，「這等同從千萬計人手中剝奪有效的教育工具」。他憂慮，這會影響保育長頸鹿的努力，已將facebook作為後備直播平台。YouTube發言人承認曾將影片下架，但稱發現舉報不當後已將影片重新上架，強調由於影片上載量極多，類似誤報偶有發生。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00005/1488120684080#sthash.uwDEJ67m.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00005%2F1488120684080%23sthash.uwDEJ67m.dpuf&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c804fd41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00005%2F1488120684080%23sthash.uwDEJ67m.dpuf&h=e2bd2f98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00005/1488120684080#sthash.uwDEJ67m.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"5bd921f54c4712823cdef831ce211ac409653b47","tid":143863,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"自己諗衰野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63218df124de8821b9fd1934bf01457ee26f8bc","tid":143863,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb43fabec4657d32e21a449503665537a314f6","tid":143863,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲撚早貼下啲貓貓狗狗圖都比人當ban圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dc4383d66f477cb0408e327a403ac4b1807766","tid":143863,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"唔係咁攪笑下話"},{"pid":"f3b4912e69acc9a5fbf0e841422578b3137d8f89","tid":143863,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"下次洗唔洗幫動物著衫"},{"pid":"371452f54f7189ee6bd10094f9ce5434d2ac3ab7","tid":143863,"uid":23535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"好多餵人奶片都冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動物生仔就色情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e117d4c69f7e49871463e8f8219072def6ab6676","tid":143863,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"國家地理頻道=全球最大AV台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe00c5487e886e8ab75212cf82ef8f96893c6f8","tid":143863,"uid":2270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國家地理頻道=全球最大AV台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb66dbeea0c6ab51c3b8c8838720046b6bcdbcb","tid":143863,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"點解可以反智成咁"},{"pid":"1cd5105e798dc2ffa81004f28b651b16b61dd917","tid":143863,"uid"